headline.main: 18 NETHERLANDERS IN REPRISAL NET; One Is Executed for Murder and Sabotage and 17 More Are Condemned to Death PAMPHLETS ARE SEIZED Propaganda Charged Against Victims Held Damaging to the Occupying Forces

lead_paragraph: LONDON, Feb. 1 (U.P.) -- One Netherlander has been executed for murder and sabotage and seventeen others have been condemned to death for distributing anti-German pamphlets, the Netherlands News Agency said today.
abstract: Gers execute J H Kleviet for slaying Netherland Nazi's wife and attempted sabotage and condemn 17 others for distributing anti-Ger pamphlets
